<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>상담사 프로필 페이지</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Pretendard-Regular', sans-serif;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .main-container {
            display: flex;
            max-width: 768px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .profile-card {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .profile-image {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            background: url('https://i.imgur.com/3beQH5s.jpeg') no-repeat center center; /* 이미지 URL 변경 필요 */
            background-size: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 5px solid #fff; /* 배경과 같은 색으로 테두리를 줘서 마치 matting 효과 */
        }
        .profile-details {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .profile-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .profile-bio {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .messages-container {
            width: 100%;
        }
        .message {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="profile-card">
            <div class="profile-image"></div>
            <div class="profile-details">
                <h2 class="profile-name">오은영</h2>
                <p class="profile-bio">안녕하세요. 저는 오은영입니다. 심리학 전문가로 활동하고 있습니다.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="messages-container">
            <h3>오은영 상담사님에게 남긴 방명록</h3>
